name: karen angulo
text: Love it! best volleyball club in Alabama, very professional and experienced coaching stuff. 100% recommend it, you will see your kid improvement very soon. Want your kid to have fun, to learn the sport,  be able to play in school and later on play in college? This is the right fit for you and your kid!

name: Randy Silver
text:
Nice facility for volleyball. Clean inside and safe parking. No air conditioning but plenty of fans to make it comfortable.
No outdoor lighting so be cautious at night.
